Contact Juerg Luterbacher (juerg@giub.unibe.ch) for further information, other reconstructed atmospheric circulation indices and reprints.
Reconstructed monthly NAO index back to December 1658
Note, the monthly values from December 1658 to November 1900 are our
reconstructions, the data from December 1900 to July 2001
are derived from Trenberth and Paolino (1980, updated, data are available through: http://dss.ucar.edu/datasets/ds010.1/data/)
